Frontend, upload ulang hasil build `dist/` ke `/home/sagalab1/public_html`.

Backend, upload ulang file/folder berikut ke `/home/sagalab1/sagalabimbel-api`:

- `index.js`
- `package.json`
- `package-lock.json`
- `tsconfig.json`
- `src/`
- `prisma/schema.prisma`
- `prisma/migrations/20260606090000_add_username_login/`
- `prisma/migrations/20260606091000_remove_google_oauth/`
